elKey`\n308:   - `SandboxNameLabelKey`\n309:   - `ManagedByLabel`\n310:   - `IdleTimeoutAnnotationKey`\n311:   - `SandboxPodNameAnnotationKey`\n312: \n313: **Verification Command:**\n314: ```bash\n315: go build ./pkg/workloadmanager/... && echo \"Constants compile OK\"\n316: ```\n317: \n318: ---\n319: \n320: ## Task 15: Add Utility Functions\n321: **Verifiable Output:** Helper functions in `pkg/workloadmanager/utils.go`\n322: \n323: - [ ] Implement `RandString(n int) string` - generates n-character random lowercase string\n324: - [ ] Implement context key types and helpers for:\n325:   - `contextKeyUserToken`\n326:   - `contextKeyServiceAccount`\n327:   - `contextKeyServiceAccountName`\n328:   - `contextKeyNamespace`\n329: - [ ] Write unit tests\n330:   - Verify test: RandString generates correct length\n331:   - Verify test: RandString generates only lowercase letters\n332: \n333: **Verification Command:**\n334: ```bash\n335: go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v -run \"TestRandString|TestContext\"\n336: ```\n337: \n338: ---\n339: \n340: ## Task 16: Route Registration\n341: **Verifiable Output:** Routes registered in HTTP server\n342: \n343: - [ ] Register `POST /v1/agent-runtime` route\n344: - [ ] Register `POST /v1/code-interpreter` route\n345: - [ ] Wire handlers to routes in server initialization\n346: - [ ] Verify routes are accessible\n347: \n348: **Verification Command:**\n349: ```bash\n350: curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/v1/agent-runtime -d '{}' -v 2>&1 | grep \"HTTP/1.1\"\n351: ```\n352: \n353: ---\n354: \n355: ## Task 17: Handler Error Response Tests\n356: **Verifiable Output:** All error paths tested\n357: \n358: - [ ] Test 400 Bad Request cases:\n359:   - Invalid JSON body\n360:   - Missing name field\n361:   - Missing namespace field\n362:   - Missing podTemplate\n363: - [ ] Test 404 Not Found cases:\n364:   - AgentRuntime not found\n365:   - CodeInterpreter not found\n366: - [ ] Test 500 Internal Server Error cases:\n367:   - Store connection failu