eted\n126: - [ ] Code follows project naming conventions (PascalCase structs, camelCase JSON tags)\n127: - [ ] All types have proper kubebuilder markers\n128: - [ ] Constants are well-documented with descriptive comments\n129: - [ ] DeepCopy methods generated for all shared types\n130: - [ ] Compatible with AR-001 and AR-002 patterns\n131: - [ ] No circular dependencies introduced\n\n(End of file - total 131 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-003 Tasks: CRD Shared Types and Constants\n\n> **Module:** `pkg/apis`  \n> **Language:** Go  \n> **Size:** S  \n> **Stage:** ST-3 completed\n\n---\n\n## Task 1: Create common_types.go\n**Verifiable Output:** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/common_types.go` exists with shared type definitions\n\n- [ ] Create `common_types.go` file in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n- [ ] Define `RuntimePhase` enum type with values: Pending, Running, Succeeded, Failed, Unknown\n- [ ] Add `// +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=Pending;Running;Succeeded;Failed;Unknown` marker\n- [ ] Define `Condition` struct with fields: Type, Status, Reason, Message, LastTransitionTime\n- [ ] Define `ConditionType` string type\n- [ ] Define `ConditionStatus` string type with constants: ConditionTrue, ConditionFalse, ConditionUnknown\n- [ ] Define `SecretKeySelector` struct with fields: LocalObjectReference, Key\n- [ ] Define `ConfigMapKeySelector` struct with fields: LocalObjectReference, Key","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-003/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775852056925,"end":1775852056947}}}}
